casebody.data:
Michael RANKINS
v.
Michael McARTHUR, Clerk of Superior Court. No. 425P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 17, 2004. Michael Rankins, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Frank R. Parrish, District Attorney, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 12th day of August 2004 in this matter for a writ of mandamus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Chowan County:

"Denied by order of the Court in Conference this the 17th day of August 2004."
